longBusinessSummary: Sanathan Textiles Limited manufactures and supplies yarn in India and internationally. The company offers polyester and cotton yarn products, and yarns for technical textiles. It also provides dope dyed, superfine/micro, functional, industrial and technical yarn, cationic dyeable, and specialty yarn products. The company was incorporated in 2005 and is based in Mumbai, India.
